<div class="moto">
	<div class="motowrap">
		<div class="topribbon"><img src="images/headertitle.png" alt="" /></div>
		<h1>On 11/16, Congress holds hearings on the first American Internet censorship system.</h1>
		<h1>This bill can pass. If it does the Internet and free speech will never be the same:</h1>
	</div>
