				  <input type="image" src="images/signupbtn.png" class="send" />
        </form>
        <p>
          Or <a href="http://act.fightforthefuture.org/page/speakout/american-censorship" title="Write congress to stop this bill!">Write Congress Now</a>
        </p>
			</div>
			<div class="participateinfo">
				<h4>What it means to participate as a site:</h4>
				<ul>
          <li>Sign up above, we'll send you code snippets when they're ready</li>
          <li>Paste the code we provide into your page</li>
          <li>Option 1: All US users (according to <a href="http://www.maxmind.com/app/geoip_country">GeoIP service</a>) will see the message to the left</li>
          <li>Option 2: Turn your site logo black (as if it were redacted), and link to a write/call Congress page.
          <li>They can close or click past it at any time</li>
          <li>Users only see the message once per site</li>
          <li>They can write and call their representatives without leaving your site</li>
          <li>When they're done, we ask them to like your site on Facebook as a thank you for taking a stand</li>
				</ul>
				<p>Any questions or ideas? <a href="mailto:protest@fightforthefuture.org">Contact us</a>!</p>
